=== 20世纪初 ===
許多蒸汽龐克的作品誕生在蒸汽龐克這一詞出現之前。該類型的電影最早有[[弗里茨·朗|弗里茨·朗]]的電影《[[大都會_(1927年電影)|大都會]]》，重要的蒸汽龐克早期代表作之一，代表了蒸汽龐克作為一種新興風格流派的誕生。[[馬溫·皮克|馬溫·皮克]]的小說{{Link-en|Titus Alone|Titus Alone}}，預料到了許多蒸汽龐克的隱喻。<ref>{{cite book|first=Lucy|last=Daniel|title=Defining Moments in Books: The Greatest Books, Writers, Characters, Passages and Events that Shook the Literary World|page=439|publisher=Cassell Illustrated|year=2007|location=US|isbn= 1-84403-605-7}}</ref>{{Link-en|雷梅迪奧斯·瓦羅|Remedios Varo}}的畫作結合了許多維多利亞時代的服飾、幻想和科幻意象。<ref>{{en}}{{cite book|last=Kaplan|first=Janet|title=Remedios Varo: Unexpected Journeys| isbn=0-7892-0627-7|publisher=Abbeville Press|year=2010}}</ref>蒸汽龐克作為主流表現最早是在[[哥倫比亞廣播公司|哥倫比亞廣播公司]]的電視劇《{{Link-en|The Wild Wild West|The Wild Wild West}}》，電影《[[飆風戰警|飆風戰警]]》（''Wild Wild West''）就是受該劇啟發而製作。<ref name="HSW steampunk" /><ref name="Grossman">{{en}}{{cite news | first=Lev | last=Grossman | title=Steampunk: Reclaiming Tech for the Masses | url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1945343,00.html | publisher=''[[Time_(magazine)|Time]]'' | date=2009-12-14 | accessdate=2009-12-10 | authorlink=Lev Grossman | archive-date=2009-12-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091209022518/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1945343,00.html | dead-url=yes }}</ref>{{Link-en|邁克爾·摩考克|Michael Moorcock}}的《{{Link-en|A Nomad of the Time Streams|A Nomad of the Time Streams}}》三部曲也是一個具有影響力的作品。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | author = Bebergal, Peter | publisher = ''[[The_Boston_Globe|The Boston Globe]]'' | title = The age of steampunk | date = 2007-08-26 | url = http://www.boston.com/news/globe/ideas/articles/2007/08/26/the_age_of_steampunk/ | accessdate = 2008-05-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080505040938/http://www.boston.com/news/globe/ideas/articles/2007/08/26/the_age_of_steampunk/ | archivedate =2008-05-05| deadurl = no }}</ref>另外，《[[妙想天開|妙想天開]]》也是早期對蒸汽龐克風格形成有著重要影響的電影。<ref name="La Ferla">{{en}}{{cite news | last = La Ferla | first = Ruth | publisher = ''[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]'' | title = Steampunk Moves Between 2 Worlds | date = 2008-05-08 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/08/fashion/08PUNK.html | accessdate = 2010-11-21 | archive-date = 2021-04-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210427213949/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/08/fashion/08PUNK.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Braiker">{{en}}{{cite news | author = Braiker, Brian | publisher = ''[[Newsweek|Newsweek]]'' | title = Steampunking Technology: A subculture hand-tools today's gadgets with Victorian style | date = 2007-10-31 | url = http://www.newsweek.com/2007/10/30/steampunking-technology.html | accessdate = 2010-11-21 | postscript = . | archive-date = 2010-11-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101114095424/http://www.newsweek.com/2007/10/30/steampunking-technology.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

=== 「蒸汽龐克」一詞的起源 ===
雖然許多在20世紀60年代和70年代出版的作品目前認定對這種風格有著重大影響，但「蒸汽龐克」這一詞作為[[赛博朋克|賽博龐克]]的變體起源於20世紀80年代後期。由科幻小說作家{{Link-en|K·W·傑特|K. W. Jeter}}創造，他試圖與{{Link-en|提姆·鮑爾斯|Tim Powers}}、{{Link-en|詹姆斯·布萊洛克|James Blaylock}}對他們和自己的作品尋找一個統稱，作品的時空背景都設定於19世紀（多為維多利亞時期），並模仿維多利亞時代科幻小說的傳統，例如赫伯特·喬治·威爾斯的《[[時間機器_(小說)|時間機器]]》。

