=== 艺术、时尚与设计 ===
蒸汽龐克的設計強調形式和功能之間的平衡<ref name=hampton1>{{en}}{{cite news|date=2008-08-01|accessdate=2012-03-06|title=Steampunk Art And Design Exhibits In The Hamptons|first=Eileen|last=Casey|url=http://www.hamptons.com/detail.php?articleID=4486|work=Hamptons Online}}</ref>，就像[[艺术与工艺美术运动|艺术与工艺美术运动]]。

=== 文学 ===
1981年的教育書籍《Elementary BASIC - Learning to Program Your Computer in BASIC with Sherlock Holmes》是第一個把[[查尔斯·巴贝奇|查理斯·巴貝奇]]的[[分析機|分析機]]作為故事進行描寫的作品。書本針對程式設計學生，描述了[[歇洛克·福尔摩斯|福爾摩斯]]在調查過程中利用分析機，並提供程式清單進行簡單的資料處理。

== 社会文化 ==
[[File:CarnevaleSteampunk.JPG|thumb]]
由於蒸汽龐克的普及，日益擴大的趨勢使蒸汽龐克成為了一種文化和生活方式。<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | last = Kaye | first = Marco | title = Mom, Dad, I'm Into Steampunk | date = 2008-07-25 | url = http://www.mcsweeneys.net/links/monologues/25steampunk.html | accessdate = 2008-08-04 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080804235630/http://www.mcsweeneys.net/links/monologues/25steampunk.html | archivedate =2008-08-04}}</ref>一些愛好者們採用蒸汽龐克美學，<ref>{{en}}{{cite web | author = Rauchfuss, Marcus | title = 蒸汽龐克美學 | date = 2008-07-01 | url = http://www.dailysteampunk.com/Steampunk%20Aesthetics.html | accessdate = 2010-02-09 | archive-date = 2008-05-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080531032150/http://www.dailysteampunk.com/Steampunk%20Aesthetics.html | dead-url = yes }}</ref>涉及時尚、家居裝飾、音樂和電影等方面。這可能被描述為{{Link-en|新維多利亞風格|Neo-Victorian}}，一種將維多利亞時代的審美原則和現代鑒賞力和技術相結合的風格。<ref name="La Ferla"/>

有些人提出了一個蒸汽龐克理念，有著龐克的反叛特徵，但這是對歷史的反叛，改變歷史的走向，通常能帶動起樂觀情緒，主題上也積極向上。<ref>{{cite web | last = Swerlick | first = Andrew | title = Technology Gets Steampunk'd | date = 2007-05-11 | url = http://www.emorywheel.com/detail.php?n=24611 | accessdate = 2008-08-04 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071209175637/http://www.emorywheel.com/detail.php?n=24611 | archivedate =2007-12-09}}</ref> 

蒸汽龐克時尚沒有特定準則，但往往將維多利亞時代風格和現代風格融合在一起。其中可能包括禮服、[[束腹|緊身胸衣]]、[[襯裙|襯裙]]、[[巴斯爾裙襯|巴斯爾裙襯]]、[[背心|背心]]、大衣、[[大禮帽|大禮帽]]和{{Link-en|鞋罩|Spats (footwear)}}或軍裝。蒸汽龐克服飾通常帶有工藝的具有時代特徵的配飾：[[齒輪|齒輪]]、[[鐘錶|鐘錶]]、[[遮陽傘|遮陽傘]]、[[護目鏡|護目鏡]]、[[鐳射槍|鐳射槍]]、[[壓力錶|壓力錶]]等。現代設備如手機、音樂播放機等也可以將外觀改造成維多利亞時代的風格。蒸汽龐克時尚形勢已影響到主流高級時裝、[[蘿莉塔時尚|蘿莉塔時尚]]、{{Link-en|貴族風格|Aristocrat (fashion)}}、新維多利亞風格和浪漫主義哥特亞文化。<ref name="La Ferla"/><ref name="Rowe">{{en}}{{cite web | title = What Is Steampunk? A Subculture Infiltrating Films, Music, Fashion, More | first = Andrew Ross | last = Rowe | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1595812/20080929/index.jhtml | publisher = MTV | date = 2008-09-29 | accessdate = 2008-10-14 | archive-date = 2012-02-04 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/65CSqkXYu?url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1595812/steampunk-subculture-looks-poised-move-above-ground.jhtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>

